      <h1>Overlay attachments policy</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Several v3 overlays carry unstructured attachments today — TA10 plans, EPCs,
        leasehold packs, photographs, identity-verification documents. This page is
        the published handling policy: file-format requirements, signing and integrity
        rules, retention guidance for issuers, and consent semantics for consumers
        whose documents are flowing through the framework.
      </p>

      <div class="callout callout--warn">
        <div class="callout__label">Draft — content pending</div>
