        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="callout callout--info">
        <div class="callout__label">Draft for Technical WG review (with C&amp;R WG input on retention + consent) — 2026-05-18</div>
        <p>
          This page synthesises <a href="/resource?path=docs/adr/0001-adopt-dcam-dmbok-elements.md">ADR 0001</a>'s
          <em>Document &amp; Content Management</em> reassessment, the production
          PDTF v3 overlay schemas, and UK GDPR retention principles into an
          attachment-handling policy <em>shape</em>. It is deliberately partial: the
          <em>shape</em> is here for working-group review; specific retention
